  "Exterior – Protection","Exterior – Lighting","Exterior – Storage & Cargo",
  "Exterior – Access & Entry","Exterior – Recovery",
  "Interior – Storage","Interior – Mounting & Tech","Interior – Comfort & Utility",
  "Drivetrain & Suspension","Other",
